name: Popis playing
description: Animation made on May 9th 2021. Here Popis is playing with a mouse in a stick, she really likes to play with it! Popis is a female cat found starving and almost dying on the streets of Santiago de Chile, by buying this NFT you will help us raise her as she deserves, we'll use 100% of the funds to buy food, vaccines and her overall health expenses, in return we'll be updating you about her status by updating photos and videos on her social networks! Thanks for helping us and greetings from Chile <3
